Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样突破舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam请专心保护母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重复  Gundam请专心保护母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军发来的通信？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是马内金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了  九条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蒂·马内金…  为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是为了给A-LAWS断罪而利用你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等这场战斗结束后再找你们问罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通知所有部队！ 立即进行回避动作！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！  攻击来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不祥的光线！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,后方出现强烈能源反应！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,改革者！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗停止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  刚才那巨大的光线是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始准备第二次扫射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  开始进行GN-Drive的更换作业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光学迷彩解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各自报告受损情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托勒密  右舷损伤轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔隆  运输舰1艘被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MS好像也有20台以上受到重创
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,A-LAWS舰队已开始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,显示到屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…  那些家伙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殖民地型外太空航行母舰  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奥利亚在2个世纪以前就预见到与未知种族的遭遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,及「即将到来的对话」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GN-Drive  吠陀  改革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船才是人类的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将人类从灭亡中拯救出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是所谓的「方舟」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通知各舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Celestial Being接下来将开始对敌方大型母舰的进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并进行将那里的量子型演算系统——吠陀夺回的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里对一直帮助我们到现在的各位表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并对战死的人们表示哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丽莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉塞  把托勒密的航向调整为敌方母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  把航向修正为敌方母舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回吠陀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最坏的情况  即使将其破坏也要阻止敌母舰的行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了即将到来的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为我们之前改变世界的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把世界从改革者的支配下解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再次改变世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GN Field  最大展开！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的任务  开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,356)\fs22}Last mission
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(416,356)\fs22}Start！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰在探索入侵路线的同时前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各Gundam攻击炮台以确保进攻路线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  打开进攻路线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大型炮台锁定这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克恩！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到我们出场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有Gaga部队就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就留到关键时刻吧  希琳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在进攻路线上的敌粒子炮已排除57%了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有新的MS部队来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是新型机吗！ 而且数量还这么多！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那形状…难道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就被自己的技术毁灭吧  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是TRANS-AM？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这数量！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的MS径直朝我们冲来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是特攻兵器！ 将炮击集中在右舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,普特利麦奥斯被…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,菲露特  找到入侵点了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使要将本舰当作盾也要守住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让他们被击沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔隆！ 卡蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么  九条！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快继续执行任务！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,右舷后方有敌机！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准对我家的上校——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,——出手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里克！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你  卡蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里克！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是舰船用船坞的入口！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用TRANS-AM一口气加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突击进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将GN-Field在舰首集中展开！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托勒密成功着陆！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer-Arios  进行托勒密的防卫！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始扫描敌人母舰  寻找吠陀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去0 Gundam那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依照战术安排  我们分散开侵入敌人母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使入侵到内部  以MS短兵相接也要夺回吠陀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大量自动机器人过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有MS！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关闭所有隔离壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉塞  伊恩  准备应战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备入侵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休想得逞  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那机体…就是它将哥哥…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧！ Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗！ 启动浮游步枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么窄的地方  你们也用不了TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自动机器人突破了隔离壁  侵入本舰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,菲露特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到吠陀了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将位置传送给Meister！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好  菲露特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,压轴的上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再让你前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别来碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧  李维夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然战争就是要短兵相接才行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,口出狂言！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就再杀你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  开Gundam的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,灭了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余粒子量不多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽  对接吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通向舰桥的隔离壁被打破了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,菲露特  米蕾娜  按照战术进行应对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要守住  这一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比利！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九条…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如此强劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是扰乱世界的罪恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没有了你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能幸福吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不断战斗而赢得的未来  并不是真正的未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们相互理解  才能筑起未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在前去掩护哈莱维准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…该不会！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人类正面临考验
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是灭亡  还是重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  决定这一切的并不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚·埃德！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.01,0:24:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,激战持续着  就在生命即将消亡之时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM Raiser的闪光打开了新世界的初啼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  「BEYOND」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那  成为革新者
